{
  "stem": "27507.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept in pretty isolated peasants' houses in-- and those peasants' houses, I still remember some of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, after two or three days, we came near to the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, a whole group of-- of people were formed with a guide, or even two guides.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to walk that night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that night we crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It took a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- but first of all, the walk was very long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was about 30 kilometers all together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to walk in-- in a file, in a-- in an Indian file.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whenever there was-- we were coming near the border post or-- or there was a danger of a patrol, we would need to fall down and lie down and not make a sound.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was still-- there was snow around still, although it was already April.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it took a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were lying down for quite often and waiting for-- until the guide gave the sing that it was possible to continue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And doing that, we came to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was barbed wire and big fencing of barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the-- they lifted somehow the bottom wires and crawled under.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And children, that's me and another child, I think, were thrown over the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this way we crossed it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we found ourselves in the German part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think-- and next years I remember well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were-- again, we walked for the remainder of the night and finally came to the peasants' house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in this peasants' house, after I think a pretty short time, suddenly a Polish police appeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They must have found us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Either somebody told them.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
